SubjectHIV - infected persons and Thalidomide Victims Assistance Order ** Amendments ** definitions/prolongation
PrecisAmendments to the HIV-INFECTED PERSONS AND THALIDOMIDE VICTIMS ASSISTANCE ORDER which revise the definition of thalidomide deformities, extend the period during which applications for assistance will be accepted and increase the total amount of available assistance.
